long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
NotionSync: Convert YouTube videos into Notion notes - FREE
Get instant, organized notes from any YouTube video:

- Auto-generate concise keypoints
- Export full transcripts with one click
- Save directly to Notion - no copy/pasting
- Perfect for students, researchers, and content creators
- 100% Free - no hidden fees or limits

Turn video content into actionable knowledge. Whether you're studying, researching, or collecting ideas, NotionSynchelps you capture and organize information from YouTube videos effortlessly in your Notion workspace.
Save hours of manual transcription and note-taking. Install now and transform how you learn from YouTube!
